  <brief_title>Effects of Pomegranate Juice on Oxidative Stress in Patients With type2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Pomegranate Juice Consumption on Glycemic Control, Lipid Profile, Oxidative Stress and Blood Pressure in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
